  "prompt": "Does any member of a Instagram group see the message I send?",
  "response": "In an Instagram group chat, every member of that group can see the messages you send. If you send a message in the group, all participants will receive it and be able to read it. However, keep in mind that if someone has muted notifications for the group, they may not see your message right away, but it will still be available for them to view later in the chat history.",
